\"font-size: 18px;\">注意:下载所录制的视频需要用浏览器打开播放，不要用软件播放</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>直接下载插件解压就可以使用了，里面还有注释帮助你们快速理解与上手操作。<br></p>                                      \r\n                        <ul class=\"x-top\" style=\"padding-left:0px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f zhs\"><span class=\"jg35\">PREVIOUS:</span></div>\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f txtRight zhs\"><span class=\"jg352\">NEXT:</span></div>\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f\">\n<a class=\"PREVIOUS\" href=\"https://www.jq22.com/jquery-info23047\"> 基于echarts大数据统计模板 </a> </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f txtRight\">\n<a class=\"NEXT\" href=\"https://www.jq22.com/jquery-info23045\"> 调节音量设计(原创) </a> </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"dr\"></div>\r\n                            <div class=\"df\"></div>\r\n                        </ul>', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 'https://www.jq22.com/jquery-info23046', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1771815925, 1771815925);
