dia/mp4\";</pre>\n<p>/*这一步判断他是什么浏览器，调用不同的格式的视频（这里以mp4为例子）*/</p>\n<pre class=\"brush:js;toolbar:false\">var xzdz=\".mp4\";\r\nvids.src=csdz+xzdz;</pre>\n<p>(路径是拼接出来的.如果需要ogg格式的,只需改&gt;&gt;&gt;xzdz即可)</p>                                      \r\n                        <ul class=\"x-top\" style=\"padding-left:0px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f zhs\"><span class=\"jg35\">PREVIOUS:</span></div>\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f txtRight zhs\"><span class=\"jg352\">NEXT:</span></div>\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f\">\n<a class=\"PREVIOUS\" href=\"https://www.jq22.com/jquery-info15264\"> jQuery放大镜插件cloudzoom.js </a> </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"fy f txtRight\">\n<a class=\"NEXT\" href=\"https://www.jq22.com/jquery-info15259\"> 简单的jQuery音乐播放器 </a> </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"dr\"></div>\r\n                            <div class=\"df\"></div>\r\n                        </ul>', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 'https://www.jq22.com/jquery-info15263', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1771816104, 1771816104);
